By Sampson Unamka Following the success of the first leg of the Johnny’s Room Live 2019 concert h Lagos in October, alternative-rock singer Johnny Drille is set to hold the Abuja and Benin edition of Johnny’s Room Live. The Abuja concert will hold on Sunday, December 8, at Central Park, Garki 1, by 5 pm. The Benin edition, tagged: ‘Homecoming’, will be held on December 15, at Image Gardens, Boundary Road, Benin, by 5 pm.  